	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Carried a Lex de sponsu (Gaius 3.121-123, FIRA 2.127; 4.22 and 109, FIRA 2.154, and 195; Ulpian fr. in FIRA 2.308f.) which preceded a Lex Cicereia and followed a Lex Appuleia (see above on these). See Niccolini, FTP 396f." .
